{"tid":708738,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解會話睇書會智商高啲思考多左 上網唔會","createTime":"2018-06-19T13:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T04:26:10.000Z","uid":82541,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fd1d97a72987be401bcb5dce6beb2049c2eb24d9","tid":708738,"uid":82541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:49:42.000Z","msg":"睇書又係接收資訊同訊息<br />\n上網睇post又係接收資訊同訊息<br />\n<br />\n點解睇書會令人思考多左智商好啲<br />\n但係上網睇資訊就唔會？ 反而會話令人唔識思考？"},{"pid":"c0fc2710521a51984ce9a2aca7060c8057fb874c","tid":708738,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"你個研究邊到睇返黎?"},{"pid":"88ea6db222ee5ac2f3d9f3ba84026d0bbb0ecc1f","tid":708738,"uid":12633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"咁上網睇書，智商會高左定低左？<br />\n<br />\n解答到呢條問題，就解答完樓主既問題。"},{"pid":"6f749f6bb1bb620ea6e1033a54bd2106e3607ac0","tid":708738,"uid":50060,"like":49,"dislike":3,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:07:57.000Z","msg":"你睇書<br />\n本書係由專家 寫左十幾二十年 嘔心瀝血既作品<br />\n<br />\n你上網睇連登<br />\n講既野係由唔經大腦, 細過20歲既小朋友 用左一分鐘都唔洗就鳩UP出黎既結果<br />\n<br />\n咁點同"},{"pid":"a7fccfc88016de3a6a6d8b77dceddd95a8827a70","tid":708738,"uid":105364,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:08:03.000Z","msg":"睇書又要睇下你睇咩書<br />\n上網又要睇下你上咩網<br />\n<br />\n根本個研究都on9"},{"pid":"68b2efa9af4130aafeea756581f61b966e6a1f31","tid":708738,"uid":191338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:09:51.000Z","msg":"睇書會刺激大腦去幻想個空間同畫面<br />\n從而令大腦更加活躍<br />\n而上網就要睇你點上法<br />\n齋接收缺乏思考個人就會越黎越numb"},{"pid":"a8aa5d33fb6bb8fc03b5af610eb63c758de45ab5","tid":708738,"uid":41813,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"睇書你會睇邏輯學哲學文學<br />\n你上網咪又係睇連登仔廢嗡"},{"pid":"db7241f47dfbdac7ebfeb48e481c871734b4bff0","tid":708738,"uid":82541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68b2efa9af4130aafeea756581f61b966e6a1f31","tid":708738,"uid":191338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:09:51.000Z","msg":"睇書會刺激大腦去幻想個空間同畫面<br />\n從而令大腦更加活躍<br />\n而上網就要睇你點上法<br />\n齋接收缺乏思考個人就會越黎越numb"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:21:37.000Z","msg":"Ching講得岩<br />\n其實我唔係睇咩研究 <br />\n只不過見人係網上面咁講 所以想問下 冇諗得太深入<br />\n於是頭先上網好快咁睇下啲文 利申：唔係研究<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bigthink.com/21st-century-spirituality/reading-rewires-your-brain-for-more-intelligence-and-empathy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbigthink.com%2F21st-century-spirituality%2Freading-rewires-your-brain-for-more-intelligence-and-empathy&d=ZgTJDYtF54CW5Yu6zMH7zrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=1bb0f4b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bigthink.com/21st-century-spirituality/reading-rewires-your-brain-for-more-intelligence-and-empathy</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.smh.com.au/technology/how-the-internet-makes-us-stupid-20100909-15383.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smh.com.au%2Ftechnology%2Fhow-the-internet-makes-us-stupid-20100909-15383.html&d=ZgTJDYtF54CW5Yu6zMH7zrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=72946345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.smh.com.au/technology/how-the-internet-makes-us-stupid-20100909-15383.html</a><br />\n<br />\n其實又真係好取決於我地上網睇咩 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未諗清就問左個咁白痴既問題"},{"pid":"5032e7d1831fa44b6e943df0e30d36694ff76824","tid":708738,"uid":82541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f749f6bb1bb620ea6e1033a54bd2106e3607ac0","tid":708738,"uid":50060,"like":49,"dislike":3,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:07:57.000Z","msg":"你睇書<br />\n本書係由專家 寫左十幾二十年 嘔心瀝血既作品<br />\n<br />\n你上網睇連登<br />\n講既野係由唔經大腦, 細過20歲既小朋友 用左一分鐘都唔洗就鳩UP出黎既結果<br />\n<br />\n咁點同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"但原來睇返上面兩篇文講既野 <br />\n其實內容可能只係其中一個原因 佢提得好少<br />\n佢強調左 原來係因為網上既資訊太多同太易令我地分心而令我地思考變鈍"},{"pid":"ba7c304d0dca9547a1c6f0f922614ac2e2eb4fd1","tid":708738,"uid":8